msgid "Are you sure you'll be okay?"
msgstr "本当に大丈夫なの？"

msgid "Yeah for sure!"
msgstr "ああ、もちろん！"

msgid "Tip top shape."
msgstr "絶好調さ。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "Take your time."
msgstr "ゆっくり行くといい。"

msgid "I mean... it's not like I'm bleeding out or anything."
msgstr "別に……俺が失血死しかけてるわけでもないんだしな。"

msgid "(I need to find an exit fast.)"
msgstr "(早く出口を見つけないと。)"

msgid "Sai is not moving."
msgstr "サイは動いていない。"

msgid "She's back..... She's back."
msgstr "彼女が……彼女が戻ってきた。"

msgid "She's singing in my ears....."
msgstr "耳の中で歌ってる……"

msgid "Singing all the time....."
msgstr "ずっとずっと歌ってる……"

msgid "Humming..."
msgstr "ハミングして……"

msgid "Burning..."
msgstr "燃えて……"

msgid "Oh no... burning...."
msgstr "あぁ……燃えて……"

msgid "Hahahahaha....."
msgstr "アハハハハ……"

msgid "Burning."
msgstr "燃えて。"
